# ── Solver SDK installation notes ────────────────────────────────────────
#
# COMSOL Multiphysics (LiveLink for Python / REST API):
#   - Requires COMSOL licence + server installation
#   - Python client: install from COMSOL installation dir
#     pip install <COMSOL_INSTALL>/plugins/com.comsol.connect.python/comsol_api-*.whl
#   - REST API: available at http://localhost:2036 when COMSOL server is running
#   - See: docs/engineering/solver-setup.md#comsol
#
# Lumerical (Ansys Python API):
#   - Requires Lumerical FDTD/MODE licence + installation
#   - Python client: pip install from Lumerical installation dir
#   - lumapi available at <LUMERICAL_INSTALL>/api/python/
#   - See: docs/engineering/solver-setup.md#lumerical
#
# Ansys Fluent (PyFluent — pip installable):
#   pip install ansys-fluent-core       # Phase 2–3
#   pip install ansys-fluent-visualization
#   Requires Ansys licence + Fluent installation; PyFluent connects via gRPC
#
# Ansys LS-DYNA (PyDYNA — pip installable):
#   pip install ansys-dyna-core         # Phase 3
#   Requires Ansys LS-DYNA licence
